---

This firmware is based on the Remora project by Scott Alford:
https://github.com/scottalford75/Remora

Modifications for XCore407I board with Ethernet communication:
- Native STM32F4 Ethernet implementation  
- DP83848I PHY support (RMII interface)
- LwIP TCP/IP stack integration
- UDP-based communication protocol
- Hardware-specific pin mappings for XCore407I

Original Remora framework license applies to core components.